Special Features:

Face ID: Secure facial recognition for unlocking your phone and authenticating payments (Apple Pay).

Siri:  Apple's intelligent assistant can answer questions, control your phone with voice commands, and automate tasks.

Integration: Apple devices work seamlessly together. You can start tasks on your iPhone and continue them on your iPad or Mac.

Health and Fitness: The Health app tracks your fitness activity, sleep patterns, and vitals (with additional accessories).

Accessibility: Built-in features like VoiceOver, Zoom, and AssistiveTouch make iPhones usable for people with disabilities.
